title: Common Dab Stew
content:
Common Dab Stew is an item that can be obtained from cooking it in Boiling Pot in The Delectable Dab Kitchen.

It is a type of Dab Stew and rewards 5 xp per action. It is used in the Passive activities for the Chef profession.

Around 1.8 Common Dab are consumed per hour of passive activity.
